import React from 'react'

const FormRecipe = () => {
    return (
        <form>
            <label>
                Recipe name:
                <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="Grandma's Special Lasagna" />
            </label>
            <label>
                Ingredients:
                <textarea name="title" placeholder="" />
            </label>
            <label>
                Steps:
                <textarea name="title" placeholder="" />
            </label>
        </form>
    )
}

export default FormRecipe
